tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    transcript TEXT,
    sentiment_score FLOAT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TranscriptAnalytics (
    analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_id INT,
    feedback_id INT,
    analytics_results JSON,
    analytics_date TIMESTAMP
);
